  "_notes": "Third fundamental category (spec §8). Shipped 2026-05-14. Linear-multiplicative conversions only (length/mass/volume/time). Temperature is intentionally deferred — non-linear (C↔F has offset, not just factor) so the unit-conversion data model + skill need a formula path, not a single toBase factor. Add when a real consumer asks. Skill surface: builtin.unit.convert. Runtime surface deferred — calculator mini-apps that want JS access can either pull via fetch from cache or use the skill via pipeline."
